  .dv scd_end ^&uindent .in 0 .ll +.25i .ln .gv Date Revised ^&_date | XFM with scd_start v1.2/01258 .qu
.ei
  .dv scd_end ^&uindent .in 0 .ll +.25i .ln .gv Date Printed ^&_date | XFM with scd_start v1.2/01258 .qu
.fi
