		and implemented in 1997 for Gecko.
&term	03 Apr 2001 (sd) : Tweeked things and added our own SCD for self formatting!
&term	08 Aug 2006 (sd) : Fixed the lgterms start so that it defines the indented 
		variable.  Caused problems in man pages that did not have any 
		previous regular/small terms seciton.
&term	25 Jan 2008 (sd) : Added seelink to allow see also references to our stuff 
		to be links to the man page when html is generated.
&endterms

&scd_end

